CONJUNCTION RULES:

G |- A set          G |- B set
----------------------------------- &-form
G |- A & B set


G |- A & B set      G |- a : A       G |- b : B
------------------------------------------------ &-intro
G |- (a , b) : A & B


G |- p : A & B      G, x : A, y : B |- c : C
--------------------------------------------- &-elim
G |- split p {x,y}.c : C


G |- (a , b) : A & B        G, x : A, y : B |- c : C
----------------------------------------------------- &-comp
G |- split (a , b) {x,y}.c = c[x\a,y\b] : C

